manifests.contents:
bench = []
test = []
example = []

[[bin]]
path = "src/main.rs"
name = "yousofmersal_client"
test = true
doctest = true
bench = true
doc = true
plugin = false
proc-macro = false
harness = true
edition = "2021"
required-features = []

[package]
name = "yousofmersal_client"
edition = "2021"
version = "0.0.1"
authors = ["Yousof Mersal <yousof777@gmail.com>"]
description = "A client for yousofmersal.com"
autobins = true
autoexamples = true
autotests = true
autobenches = true

[dependencies]
anyhow = "1.0.69"
gloo = "0.8.0"
js-sys = "0.3.61"
log = "0.4.17"
pulldown-cmark = "0.9.2"
urlencoding = "2.1.2"
wasm-logger = "0.2.0"

[dependencies.dioxus]
version = "0.3.2"
features = ["hot-reload"]

[dependencies.dioxus-free-icons]
version = "0.6.0"
features = ["font-awesome-brands", "font-awesome-solid"]

[dependencies.dioxus-router]
version = "0.3.0"
features = ["web", "query"]

[dependencies.dioxus-toast]
git = "https://github.com/YousofMersal/dioxus-toast"
features = ["web"]
default-features = false

[dependencies.dioxus-use-storage]
git = "https://github.com/YousofMersal/dioxus-hooks"

[dependencies.dioxus-web]
version = "0.3.1"

[dependencies.fermi]
version = "0.3.0"

[dependencies.web-sys]
version = "0.3.61"
features = ["Storage"]
[profile.release]
opt-level = "z"
lto = true
codegen-units = 1
panic = "abort"

[profile.release.package]
